  },
  "**We can use these two gems on that pedestal over at the City Hall!**": {
    "translation": "我们可以把这两颗宝石放到市政厅的底座上!"
  },
  "**We fixed the button with the fuse! The door will open soon**": {
    "translation": "我们用保险丝修好了按钮!大门即将打开"
  },
  "**We found a blue gem**": {
    "translation": "我们找到了蓝色宝石"
  },
  "**This gem might be useful to us later -- Let's keep it for now**": {
    "translation": "这颗宝石以后可能有用,先留着"
  },
  "**This button's fuse is busted -- The door will not open**": {
    "translation": "这个按钮的保险丝坏了-大门不会打开"
