  "**We need to be fast before Nemesis catches up to us**": {
    "translation": "在追迹者追上来之前我们得快点行动"
  },
  "**Seems like we need a crank to roll that door open**": {
    "translation": "看来我们需要曲柄才能把门卷起来打开"
