  "**Congratulations! You have beaten the map!**": {
    "translation": "恭喜!你们通关了这张地图!"
  },
  "**What's happening to us?**": {
    "translation": "我们怎么了?"
  },
  "**This virus... it's eating us alive!**": {
    "translation": "这种病毒...正在吞噬我们的生命!"
  },
  "**Entered the correct password**": {
    "translation": "输入了正确密码"
  },
  "**Entered the incorrect password**": {
    "translation": "输入了错误密码"
  },
  "**reset**": {
    "translation": "重置"
  },
  "**Note: I left the password to the safe on the shelf of William Shakespeares Tragedies in the bookstore**": {
    "translation": "提示:我把保险箱密码放在书店书架上的莎士比亚悲剧集中."
  },
  "**Note: This zombie outbreak is similar to the one at Spencer Mansion. so I think theyre somehow related. I send you a full countdown soon**": {
    "translation": "提示:这次僵尸爆发与斯宾塞宅邸那次很像.所以我认为它们有关联.我很快把完整倒计时发给你."
  },
  "**Note: Mom disappeared somewhere and Dad went looking for her. He told me not to open the door to anyone until he returned**": {
    "translation": "提示:妈妈失踪了爸爸去找她.他让我在他回来前不要给任何人开门."
  },
  "**Note: For now I place my dolls all over the museum. My mother will be happy when she sees them**": {
    "translation": "提示:我暂时把玩偶摆在博物馆各处.妈妈看到会很开心."
  },
  "**Note: Some madman bit Robert on the arm. A policeman pulled him away and we managed to escape**": {
    "translation": "提示:有个疯子咬了罗伯特的手臂.一名警察把他拉开我们才逃出来."
  },
  "**Note: I wanted to get the rifle from the basement. but I forgot where you hid the key. We are going to the hospital and will wait for you there**": {
    "translation": "提示:我想从地下室拿步枪.但我忘了你把钥匙藏在哪.我们要去医院并在那等你."
  },
  "**Note: I put the fuse in storage. People have gone mad and are devouring each other. I advise you to leave the city at the first opportunity**": {
    "translation": "提示:我把保险丝放在仓库.人们都疯了在互相吞食.我建议一有机会就离开城市."
  },
  "**Note: Its a complete mess here. There arent enough weapons for everyone. I left a shotgun in the parking lot especially for you**": {
    "translation": "提示:这里一团糟.武器不够分给所有人.我特意在停车场给你留了一把霰弹枪."
  },
  "**Note: I hope you can make it there. Then break through to the train station**": {
    "translation": "提示:希望你能赶到那里.然后突围到火车站."
  },
  "**Note: Umbrella Corp announced a change in the primary distribution point for our products**": {
    "translation": "提示:保护伞公司宣布更改我们产品的主要配送点."
  },
  "**Note: I dont understand why they in such a rush. I send you the coordinates for their new base soon**": {
    "translation": "提示:我不明白他们为何这么着急.我很快把新基地坐标发给你."
  }
}
